Package org.texgen.textures.complex

Set of complex textures built up out of other textures

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Camouflage Camouflage texture used as the demo texture in the documentation
ComplexMarble Returns a complex marble color based on a number of composite textures
Dirty Takes an input texture and color (default black) and dirties the source using a noisy texture
DirtyBrick Returns a color based on brick texture with a dirty noise overlay on top
Fireball Takes a gradient and centers it, and moves through the gradient as u,v moves away from the center of the texture.
Flame Creates a firey marble type texture.
Map Texture to create a 2D map based on noise
MarbleChessboard A Marble chessboard texture based on the checker and two marble type textures.
NoisyTexture A Noisy texture that takes an input source and sets the alpha channel based on noise(u,v)*size; This only creates a texture with noisy transparency.
Polkadot A texture that uses a dot and background texture to create a polkdot texture.
SunEclipse Composite texture that uses the fireball to build a fireball with a planet eclipsing it.
